moto ji lintas awak nyan.
“Lôn meulumpoë keu moto,” kheun Harry, teuingat tiba-tiba.
“Nyan teungoh jiplueng.”
Paman Vernon karap keunong moto di keue. Gobnyan geuputa uneun
bak teumpat duek jih dan ji meukreuh-kreuh bak Harry, muka jih lagee bit raksasa ngon kumih:
“MOTOR BEU TERBANG!”
Dudley ngon Piers geuceu-ceu.
“Lon teupeu awak nyan hana,” kheun Harry. “Nyan lumpoe mantong.”
Teuma gobnyan meuharab that hana geupeugah sapeue. Meunyo na saboh hai nyang .
Dursleys benci bahkan leubeh nibak jih tanyong, nyan jih peugah haba teuntang
peu mantong nyang meulaku deungon cara nyang hana patot, hana peuduli meunyoe nyan lam lumpoe atawa bahkan
kartun — awaknyan deuh jih jipike gobnyan mungken meuteumé pikeran-pikeran nyang bahaya.
Bak uroe Sabtu nyan that mata uroe dan kebon binatang nyan rame that ngon keluarga. Nyan
Dursleys geubloe es krim coklat rayeuk Dudley ngon Piers bak pinto tamong ngon .
lheuh nyan, kareuna ureung inong nyang meusenyum lam van nyan ka jitanyong bak Harry peu nyang jih galak seugolom jih .
