brok, pih, Harry geupike, geujilat watee awaknyan jikalon gorila jigaruk ulee jih .
nyang deuh jih luar biasa lagee Dudley, kecuali hana pirang.
Harry na beungoh nyang paleng get lam watee nyang trep. Gobnyan that-that geuhati-hati keu .
jak bacut jiôh nibak keuluarga Dursley sampoe Dudley ngon Piers, nyang teungoh
