Batee Tukang Sihe
BAB KEULIMONG
GANG DIAGON
H arry beungoh that beungoh jih. Bah pih gobnyan hase geuteupeue bahwa uroe ka trang, .
gobnyan teutap geutop mata gobnyan.
“Nyan lumpoe, jipeugah bak droe jih deungon teuga. “Lôn meulumpoë na sidroe raksasa nyang nan jih Hagrid .
teuka geujak peugah bak lon lon jak sikula tukang sihe. Watee lon buka mata lon akan jeut keu
di rumoh lam lemari lon.”
Tiba-tiba na su nyang kreueh that.
Dan na Tante Petunia jitok pinto, pikeran Harry, hate jih .
teungoh teungoh. Teuma gobnyan mantong hana geubuka mata. Ka lheueh that jroh lumpoe nyan.
Keutok. Keutok. Keutok.
“Baiklah,” Harry menggumam, “Lon teungoh beudoh.”
Jih jiduek dan mantel brat Hagrid rhet nibak jih. Gubuk nyan peunoh ngon .
cahya mata uroe, badai ka lheuh, Hagrid keudroe teungoh teungeut bak sofa nyang ka rhet,
dan na saboh cicém hantu jipoh cakar jih ateueh jeundela, saboh koran jimat lam .
paruh.
Harry meureubot-reubot bak gaki jih, that seunang jih meurasa lagee balon rayeuk .
teungoh bengkak lam tuboh jih. Gobnyan langsong geujak bak jeundela dan geusentak jeundela nyan. Nyan
cicém hantu jiplueng dan jipeutron koran nyan ateueh Hagrid, nyang hana jibeudôh .
ateuh. Burung hantu nyan laju jiplueng-plueng u ateuh lantai dan mulai ji serang mantel Hagrid.
“Bek tapeubuet lagee nyan.”
Harry geucuba geulambai cicém hantu nyan nibak jalan, tapi cicém nyan jipoh paruh jih
galak keu jih dan laju jijak peugot mantel nyan.
“Hagrid!” kheun Harry deungon su nyang kreuh. “Na cicém hantu —”
“Bayeue jih,” Hagrid geukheun u dalam sofa.
"Peu?"
“Jih jikeuneuk bayeue keu jikirém keureutah nyan. Neukalön lam kantong-kantong.”
Mantel Hagrid deuh jih hana jipeugot sapeue seulaen kantong — tandan-tandan .
kunci, pelet siput, bola-bola tali, humbug lada, kantong teh...akhe jih, Harry
geutarek saboh jaroe koin nyang deuh jih aneh.
“Bri keu jih limong boh Knut,” kheun Hagrid ngon mengantuk.
“Kacang?”
“Nyang ubit-ubit teumaga.”
Harry geuhitong limong boh koin teumaga ubit, dan cicem hantu nyan geujok gaki jih meunan .
Harry jeuet jipeutamong peng nyan lam kantong kulet ubeut nyang jiikat bak kantong nyan. Lheueh nyan jiplueng .
rot jeundela nyang teubuka.
Hagrid geukuap ngon su nyang kreuh, geuduek, dan geurentang.
“Paleng get beu off, Harry, le that yang ta peugot uroe nyoe, harus beudoh keu London dan bloe mandum
yer barang fer sikula.”
Harry teungoh geuputa-puta koin-koin tukang sihe nyan dan geukaloen-kaloen. Gobnyan baroe
dipike keu sapeue-sapeue nyang jeuet keu rasa jih lagee balon bahagia lam droe jih .
ka keunong tusukan.
"Um - Hagrid?"
“Mm?” kheun Hagrid, nyang teungoh ji tarek bot nyang rayeuk that nyan.
“Lon hana peng — dan droeneuh neudeungo Uncle Vernon beuklam...gobnyan .
hana jibayeue keu ulôn keu lôn jak meurunoe ajaéb.”
“Bek khawatir keu nyan,” kheun Hagrid, geudong dan geugaruk-garuk .
ulee. “D’yeh pike yer ureung chik hana geutinggai yeh sapeu?”
“Teuma meunyo rumoh awaknyan ka hanco —”
“Awak nyan hana jikeubah meuh lam rumoh, aneuk agam! Nah, phon singgah fer kamoe nakeuh .
Gringot. Bank tukang sihe. Na sosis, awaknyan hana brok lupie — an' I wouldn'.
peugah hana teh bit o' yer kue ulang thon, pih hana.”
“Penyihir na bank?”
“Cuma nyang saboh. Gringot. Diplueng le bunian.”
Harry geupeutron bit sosis nyang jimat.
“Bunian?”
“Yeah — jadi yeh'd be gila ter cuba an' rampok nyan, lon akan peugah yeh nyan. Bek pernah kacau
ngon bunian, Harry. Gringotts nakeuh teumpat nyang paleng aman di donya fer peu mantong yeh .
keuneuk ter jaga aman — 'kecuali mungken Hogwarts. Seubagoe peukara o' fakta, lon gotta jak saweu
Gringotts pokok jih. Fer Dumbledor nyan. Bisnis Hogwarts.” Hagrid geugamba droe geuh
up ngon bangga. “Jih biasa jih jiteume lon ter peugot hal-hal peunteng fer jih. Meujak cok droeneuh —
meuteumee hai-hai nibak Gringotts — jiteupeue jih jeuet jipeucaya keu ulôn, kalon.”
“Ka na mandum? Ayo, meunyo meunan.”
Harry geuikot Hagrid u luwa ateuh batee. Langèt cukôp trang jinoe .
dan laôt meukilat-kilat lé cahya mata uroe. Peuraho nyang ka jisiwa le Paman Vernon mantong .
disinan, ngon le that ie di miyueb lheuh badai.
“Pakriban cara droeneuh trok usinoe?” tanyong Harry, geumita-mita saboh kapai laen.
“Terbang,” kheun Hagrid.
"Pheu?"
“Ie — tapi tanyoe tajak woe lam hai nyoe. Bukan s'pposed ter pakek sihe jinoe lon ka .
ka yeh.”
Awaknyan jiduek lam peuraho, Harry mantong jikeumalon Hagrid, jicuba
bayangkan jih jiplueng.
“Nampak jih male ter row, padahal,” kheun Hagrid, geubri Harry saboh teuk dari .
rupa jih nyang samping. “Meunyo lon ter — er — peucepat hal-hal bacut, akan yeh keberatan .
hana neuseubôt bak Hogwarts?”
“Teuntèe hana,” kheun Harry, galak that geukaloen leubèh le ajaib. Hagrid geutarek
payung pink nyan teuma, jiteupok dua goe bak binèh peuraho, dan awaknyan laju jijak .
keu arah darat.
“Pakon droeneuh jeuet keu pungo keu neucuba neujak rampok Gringotts?” tanyong Harry.
“Mantra — pesona,” kheun Hagrid, geubuka koran gobnyan bak gobnyan .
geupeugah haba. “Kheun awak nyan na naga nyang jaga lemari besi keamanan tinggi. Dan lheuh nyan yeh
gotta mita jalan yer — Gringotts na meureutoh mil di miyup London, kalon. Lhok
di miyup Miyueb Tanoh. Yeh'd matee deuk tryin' ter keudeh, bah pih yeh hana
keulola ter meurumpok yer jaroe bak summat.”
Harry geuduek dan geupike keu hai nyoe watee Hagrid geubaca koran gobnyan, koran .
Harian Nabi. Harry ka meurunoe bak Paman Vernon bahwa ureung galak ditinggai .
sidroe-droe watee awaknyan jipeubuet lagee nyoe, tapi payah that, jih hana tom na nyang le that
pertanyaan lam udep gobnyan.
“Kementerian o’ Sihir messin’ hal-hal lagee biasa,” gumam Hagrid, berbalik .
halaman nyan.
“Na Kementerian Sihir?” Harry geutanyong, sigohlom jih jeuet jitheun .
droe geuh.
“’Teuntèe,” kheun Hagrid. “Awak nyan jikeuneuk Dumbledore jeut keu Mentri, o’.
teunte, tapi jih hana tom ji tinggai Hogwarts, jadi Cornelius Fudge tuha nyan meurumpok buet nyan.
Bungler meunyo pernah na saboh. Jadi jih jipoh Dumbledore ngon cicem hantu tiep beungoh,
askin' fer nasihat.”
“Tapi peue buet saboh Kementerian Sihir?”
“Nyan, buet utama awak nyan nakeuh jijaga dari Muggles nyang mantong na .
tukang sihe an' tukang sihe ateuh an' miyueb nanggroe.”
"Pakeun?"
"Pakeun? Blimey, Harry, mandum ureung akan meuheut keu solusi ajaib keu awak nyan
masalah nyang na. Nah, geutanyoe leubeh get ta tinggai sidroe.”
Bak watèe nyoe kapai nyan meupok ngon lembut ngon bintéh pelabuhan. Hagrid
geulipat koran gobnyan, dan awaknyan jiék ateueh reunyeuen batée u jalan.
Ureueng-ureueng nyang lewat that jikeumalon Hagrid watee awaknyan jijak rot banda ubeut nyan u .
stasiun nyan. Harry hana jeuet geusalahkan awaknyan. Kon mantong Hagrid dua go leubeh manyang nibak .
soe mantong, gobnyan sabe geutunyok bak hai-hai nyang biasa-biasa mantong lagee meter parkir dan
geupeugah deungon su nyang kreueh, “Ka kalon nyan, Harry? Hal-hal nyang dilumpoe le Muggles nyoe, eh?”
“Hagrid,” kheun Harry, meudeuh-deuh bacut watee jiplueng keu jijak, “peu droeneuh neupeugah .
na naga di Gringotts?”
“Nyan, meunan kheun awak nyan,” kheun Hagrid. “Crikey, lon galak keu naga.”
“Kamoe galak keu saboh?”
"Meuheut saboh sejak lon manteng aneuk mit - nyoe tanyoe jak."
Awak nyan ka troh u stasiun. Na kereta u London bak limong .
watee 10 minit. Hagrid, nyang hana meuphom “peng Muggle,” lagee nyang geukheun le gobnyan,
geubri tagihan keu Harry mangat jeuet geubloe tiket awak nyan.
Ureueng-ureueng leubeh meutatap bak kereta. Hagrid geucok dua boh kursi dan .
duek meuikat peu nyang deuh lagee tenda sirkus warna kuneng kanari.
“Mantong na surat yer, Harry?” tanyong jih bak jikira jahitan.
Harry geucok amplop perkamen nyan lam saku gobnyan.
“Get that,” kheun Hagrid. “Na daftar disinan mandum nyang yeh peureulee.”
Harry geubuka keureutah keudua nyang hana geuperhatikan malam nyan .
sigohlom, dan baca:
SIKOLA HOGWARTS nibak SIHIH dan SIHIH .
SEURAGAM
Siswa thon phon akan geubutuhkan:
1. Lhee boh set jubah buet biasa (hitam) .
2. Saboh topi mancung poloih (hitam) keu pakek uroe .
3. Saboh pasang sarung jaroe peulindong (kulit naga atawa nyang saban)
4. Saboh jubah musim seumeu’uet (hitam, peuikat pirak) .
Neu ingat, mandum bajee aneuk murid beu na tag nan .
BUKU KURSUS .
Mandum murip haroih na saboh salinan nibak maseng-maseng nyang na di miyup nyoe:
Buku Mantra Baku (Kelas 1) nyang geutuléh lé Miranda Goshawk .
Saboh Seujarah Sihe le Bathilda Bagshot .
Teori Ajaib le Adalbert Waffling
Panduan Pemula untuk Transfigurasi oleh Saklar Emeric .
Siribee Herbal dan Jamur Ajaib oleh Spora Phyllida
Draf Ajaib dan Ramuan oleh Arsenius Jigger .
Binatang-binatang nyang luar biasa dan dipat ta teume awaknyan le Newt Scamander .
Pasukan Gelap: Panduan Peulindong Droe le Quentin Trimble
