nyan teubuka sigo-go. Dipeugah, lam saboh coretan nyang that hana rapi:
Harry nyang meutuah,
Lon teupeu droeneuh na cuti uroe Jumat seupot, jadi droeneuh galak neujak dan neujak meu
cangkie teh ngon lon sekitar lhee?
