teungoh jidong bak bangku awaknyan seudangkan Neville, nyang ka keunong basah lam ramuan .
watee kuali rhet, meurengek-rengek saket bak bisul mirah beungeh jiteubiet mandum .
ateuh jaroe ngon gaki jih.
