lam gareh-gareh nyang rapi ateuh tanoh. Harry ka geudeungo Fred ngon George Weasley geukheun
teuntang sapu sikula, peugah na nyang mulai getar meunyo ka jiplueng
manyang that, atawa sabe jiplueng bacut u wie.
