Puan Hooch. “Jaga sapu gata mangat teutap, beudoh padum-padum boh gaki, lheuh nyan teuka .
lurus keudeh u miyueb deungon cara meusandar keu ukeu bacut. Bak siul lon — lhee — dua .
—”
