“HARI PEUTEUKAT!”
Hate jih leubeh bagah rhet nibak baroe ji plueng. Profesor McGonagall nakeuh .
jiplueng u arah awaknyan. Gobnyan geudong bak gaki, geumeu-ulang-ulang.
"Hana tom — lam mandum masa lon di Hogwarts —"
