nibak dengki dan beungeh bak muka gobnyan. “Kamoe akan meutamong lam nyan kali nyoe, Potter, thon-thon phon .
hana geubri idhin keu awaknyan.”
Ron hana jeuet geulawan.
“Nyan kon sapu tuha sapeu,” kheun jih, “nyan Nimbus Dua Ribee.
