jamuan awai masa.
Harry teungoh geubantu droe geuh keu kentang panggang watee Profesor Quirrell .
teuka jiplueng-plueng u dalam aula, sorban jih miring dan teumakot bak muka jih. Mandum
meutatap bak troh bak kurusi Profesor Dumbledore, meu-ulang-ulang bak meja,
dan geukheun, “Troll — lam rumoh glab — geupike gata harôh gata teupeue.”
Gobnyan lheueh nyan karam u lantai lam keuadaan pingsan mate.
Na karu. Butuh padum-padum boh petasan ungu nyang beureutoh dari .
akhe tungkat Profesor Dumbledore keu jiba seungap.
“Prefek,” kheun gobnyan, “pimpin Rumoh-rumoh gata woe u asrama .
sigra!"
Percy na lam elemen jih.
“Ikot kheueh ulôn! Teutap meusapat, thon-thon phon! Hana peurlee teumakot keu troll meunyo droneuh .
ikot peurintah lon! Tetap toe di likot lon, jinoe. Peugot jalan, thon-thon phon teuka
reut! Meuah, lon nyoe prefek!”
“Pakriban jeut troll tamong?” tanyong Harry watee awak nyan ji ek reunyeuen.
“Bek tanyong bak lon, awak nyan seharusjih bangai that,” kheun Ron. "Mungken
Peeves geupeubiyeu nyan keu lelucon Halloween.”
Awaknyan jijak rot kelompok-kelompok ureueng nyang meulaen-laen nyang bagah-bagah u arah nyang meulaen-laen.
Bak awaknyan jijak rot kerumunan Hufflepuff nyang bingong, Harry
tiba-tiba jimat jaroe Ron.
“Lon baroe lon pike — Hermione.”
“Pakriban ngon jih?”
“Jih hana jiteupeu keu troll nyan.”
Ron jigiget bibi jih.
“Oh, ka jeut,” kheun jih. “Tapi leubeh get Percy hana geukaloen geutanyoe.”
Meu-ulang-ulang, awak nyan meugabong ngon Hufflepuffs jijak rot laen, jiplueng .
di miyueb saboh koridor samping nyang seupôt, dan bagah-bagah jijak u arah kama manoe aneuk dara. Awaknyan
