jih,” Harry geupeuingat jih.
Awak nyan ka troh bak potret Fat Lady.
“Idong bui,” kheun awaknyan laju jitamong.
Ruang umum ka peunoh ngon riyoh. Mandum ureung teungoh geupajoh makanan nyan .
nyang ka geukirém u ateueh. Hermione, kiban pih, jidong sidroe bak binèh pintô, jipreh .
