“Kamoe dua preh disinoe!” Hagrid geukheun. “Stay on the path, I'll come back
keu yeh!”
Awaknyan jideungoe jihnyan jipoh jijak rot semak-semak dan jidong .
saleng meungieng, that teumakot, sampoe hana jeuet jideungo sapeue seulaen .
meukarat ôn bak lingka awaknyan.
“You don't think they've been hurt, do you?” geubisiek le Hermione.
“Lon hana peduli meunyo Malfoy na, tapi meunyo na nyang na Neville...nyan salah kamoe
jih na disinoe bak teumpat phon.”
Menit-menit nyan ji tarek le. Their ears seemed sharper than usual. Harry nyan
seemed to be picking up every sigh of the wind, every cracking twig. Peue nyang ka
teungoh teudjadi? Pat teuma nyang la'én?
At last, a great crunching noise announced Hagrid's return. Malfoy,
Neville, dan Fang na ngon jih. Hagrid ka meu-ulang-ulang. Malfoy, deuh jih, na .
sneaked up behind Neville and grabbed him as a joke. Neville ka panik dan
geukirém u ateueh percikan api.
“Kamoe akan beruntung ter drop anythin 'jinoe, ngon raket kamoe dua nyan .
peugot'. Beutoi, kamoe meugantoe kelompok — Neville, droeneuh tinggai ngon lon an'.
Hermione, Harry, droeneuh jak ngon Fang dan 'ureung bangai nyoe. Meuah lon,” tambah Hagrid lam saboh .
bisik keu Harry, “tapi jih akan na watee nyang leubeh brat teumakot droeneuh, an' kamoe haroh
peugot nyoe.”
So Harry set off into the heart of the forest with Malfoy and Fang. Awaknyan
geujak karab sitengeh jeum, seumaken dalam uteuen, sampoe bak jalan .
became almost impossible to follow because the trees were so thick. Harry
geupike darah deuh seumaken tebal. Na percikan bak ukheue .
nibak saboh bak kayée, lagée makhluk gasien nyan ka jipoh-poh ngon sakét to ngon jih.
Harry jeut geukaloen clearing ukeu, melalui cabang-cabang kusut dari kuno
oak.
“Kalon —” gobnyan geugum-gum, geumat jaroe gobnyan keu geutheun Malfoy.
Na sapeue-sapeue nyang putéh that meukilat-kilat di ateueh tanoh. Awaknyan jijak toe.
Nyan unicorn nyan hana masalah, dan ka mate. Harry hana tom geukalon
peue-peue nyang that lagak ngon seudeh. Its long, slender legs were stuck out at odd angles
teumpat jih ka rhet dan rambut jih ka meutabu putéh mutiara ateueh ôn-ôn kayée nyang seupôt.
Harry ka geucok saboh langkah keudeh watee na su nyang meugleh geupeugot jih
beku bak teumpat jih jidong. Saboh semak di binèh blang meugeutar....Lheueh nyan, teubiet
nibak bayangan, sidroe tokoh nyang meutudung teuka jijak-jak u ateuh tanoh lagee padum-padum droe
binatang nyang jijak. Harry, Malfoy, ngen Fang teudong teudong. Sosok nyang meujubah
troh bak unicorn, geupeutron ulée jih ateueh luka bak blah binatang nyan, dan .
mulai jijieb darah jih.
“AAAAAAAAA!”
Malfoy geupeuleumah su nyang that teuga dan geubaut — meunan cit Fang. Nyang meutudung
tokoh nyan jibeudoh ulee jih dan jikeumalon tepat bak Harry — darah unicorn teungoh jiteubiet .
di miyueb bagian ukeue jih. Nyan troh bak gaki jih dan teuka deungon bagah u arah Harry — jih hana jeuet .
meugrak sabab teumakot.
Teuma sakét lagée nyang gohlom tom geurasa sigohlom nyan jitusok ulée gobnyan; nyan lagee
beukah jih ka meuapui. Siteungoh buta, jih jiteubiet-teubiet keudeh. Gobnyan geudeungo kuku
di likot jih, meugalop, dan na nyang ji plueng gleh ateuh Harry, ji charge bak
kira.
Saket ulee Harry that brat sampoe rhet bak teuot. Butuh watee si minet
atawa dua keu lewat. Watèë geungieng u ateuëh, tokoh nyan ka hana le. Saboh centaur teungoh jidong .
ateuh jih, kon Ronan atawa Bane; nyang nyoe deuh leubeh muda; jih na ôk pirang putéh
dan saboh badan palomino.
“Kamoe hana peukara?” kheun centaur nyan, sira ji tarek Harry u gaki jih.
“Ya — teurimong geunaseh — peue nyan?”
Centaur nyan hana geujaweub. Gobnyan na mata biru nyang hireuen, lagee pucat .
batée safir. Jih jikeumalon Harry deungon get, mata jih teutap bak beukah nyang teudong .
keudeh, livid, bak ulee Harry.
“Gata aneuk agam Potter,” kheun gobnyan. “Leubeh get droeneuh neuwoe bak Hagrid.
Uteuen hana aman bak masa nyoe — khusus jih keu droeneuh. Jeut neu ek? Nyan akan na
leubeh bagah cara nyoe.
“Nan lon Firenze,” tambah jih, watee ji peutron droe jih u keue .
gaki sampoe Harry jeuet jiék u punggông jih.
Tiba-tiba na su nyang leubeh galop dari blahdeh .
peugleh. Ronan and Bane came bursting through the trees, their flanks heaving
dan meuruoh.
“Apui!” Bane meugeunta. "Pu buet? Kamoe na manusia bak .
punggong droeneu! Peu kheueh gata hana malée? Peuë gata ureuëng biasa ?”
“Peu kheueh gata sadar soe nyoe?” kheun Firenze. “Nyoe keuh aneuk Potter. Nyan
leubeh bagah jih jitinggai uteuen nyoe, leubeh get.”
“Peue nyang ka gata peugah bak jih?” geukheun le Bane. “Ingat kheueh, Firenze, .
kamoe meusumpah hana kamoe peudong droe kamoe meulawan langét. Peuë hana ta baca peuë njang .
keu teuka lam gerak-gerak planet-planet?”
Ronan geujak tanoh ngon gugoe. “Lon yakin Firenze geupike gobnyan .
bertindak untuk yang terbaik, “ kheun jih deungon su yang suram.
Bane jiteugon gaki likot jih ngon beungeh.
“Keu nyang paleng jroh! Peue hubongan jih ngon geutanyoe? Centaur nyan meukaet ngon .
peue nyang ka geupeuteuntèe lé gob! Kon urusan geutanyoe ta plueng-plueng lagee keuleudei lheuh .
manusia nyang sesat lam uteuen geutanyoe!”
Firenze tiba-tiba jibeudoh bak gaki likot jih deungon beungeh, sampoe Harry harus
cok bahu jih keu teutap.
“Peu kheueh gata hana takalon unicorn nyan?” Firenze bellowed at Bane. “Peu kheueh hana .
meuphom pakon jipoh? Atawa planet-planet hana jibi gata tamong lam rahasia nyan? ulon
neuset droe keu peuë njang teungoh meu-ulang-ulang dalam uteuën njoë, Bane, ya, deungon manusia .
di samping ulôn meunyo ulôn harôh.”
Dan Firenze geujak meu-ulang-ulang; deungon Harry meucengkeram sebaik mungken,
awaknyan jiplueng u dalam bak-bak kayée, jitinggai Ronan ngon Bane di likot awaknyan.
Harry hana na petunjuk peu nyang teungoh teudjadi.
“Pakon Bane that beungeh?” geutanyong lé ureuëng nyan. “What was that thing you saved me
nibak, pokok jih?”
Firenze meulambat bak jak, geubri peuingat keu Harry untuk geujaga ulee jih meutundok mumpung.
nibak cabeueng-cabeueng nyang meugantung miyueb, tapi hana geujaweub pertanyaan Harry. Awaknyan jipeugöt awaknyan
jalan rot bak-bak kayee lam seungap that treb sampoe Harry geupike Firenze hana .
keuneuk peugah haba ngon jih le. Awaknyan teungoh jijak rot saboh teumpat nyang that padat .
patch bak kayee, namun, watee Firenze tiba-tiba jitheun.
“Harry Potter, peu gata teupeu peue darah unicorn nyan geungui?”
“Hana,” kheun Harry, teukeujot deungon pertanyaan aneh nyan. “We've only used the horn
dan ôk ikue lam Ramuan.”
“Nyan kareuna nyan saboh hai nyang monster, keu poh unicorn,” kheun Firenze.
“Hanya sidroe ureueng nyang hana sapeue nyang gadoh, dan mandum nyang jeuet jiteumee, nyang akan geupeubuet lagee nyan .
maksiet. The blood of a unicorn will keep you alive, even if you are an inch from
maté, teuma deungon harga nyang dahsyat. Kamoe ka kamoe poh sapeue-sapeue nyang murni dan hana meulaen-laen keu .
peuseulamat droe, dan droeneuh akan na tapi sitengeh udep, udep kutukan, mulai saat .
darah jisentuh bibi gata.”
Harry meutatap bak likot ulee Firenze, nyang ka meu-ulang-ulang pirak bak
cahya buleuen.
“Tapi soe nyang putôh asa that?” hek jieta-takeut lé jih. “Meunyo droeneuh neujak .
keunong kutuk keu siumu masa, leubeh get mate, kon?”
“Nyan,” Firenze setuju, “kecuali nyang peureulee nakeuh teutap udep cukop treb .
keu jieb sapeue-sapeue nyang laén — sapeue-sapeue nyang teuma jipeuwoe gata ubak teunaga nyang peunoh .
dan kuasa — sapeue-sapeue nyang teuma meumakna gata hana hase maté. Pak Potter, peu droeneuh
teupeu peue nyang teusöm lam sikula bak saat nyoe?”
“Baca Peujabat! Of course — the Elixir of Life! Tapi hana
meuphom soe —”
“Jeut neu pike hana soe nyang ka meuthon-thon neu preh kembali keu kuasa,
soe nyang ka meu-ulang-ulang, teungoh geupreh-preh kesempatan awaknyan?”
Lagee tinju beusoe ka jikeup tiba-tiba di sekitar hate Harry.
Di ateuh su-su bak kayee, jih deuh jideungoe sigo teuk peu nyang ka jipeugah le Hagrid .
gobnyan bak malam awaknyan ka meurumpok: “Na nyang peugah gobnyan meuninggai. Codswallop, meunurot lon.
Dunno meunyo gobnyan ka sep manusia nyang tinggai di gobnyan keu mate.”
“Maksud droeneuh,” Harry geukheun, “nyan Vol-”
“Hari! Harry, peue droeneuh beutoi?”
Hermione teungoh jiplueng u arah awaknyan bak jalan, Hagrid jipupoe-pupoe
di likot jih.
