lereng, “nyang Hagrid meuheut leubeh nibak nyang laen nakeuh naga, dan saboh
asing ternyata yang baru kebetulan na boh telor lam saku? Padim boh
ureung meuputa-puta ngon boh telor naga meunyo nyan meulawan ngon hukom tukang sihe? Naseb awak nyan
meurumpok Hagrid, hana neukira? Pakon hana lôn kalon dilee?”
“Peue nyang gata peugah?” kheun Ron, tapi Harry, jiplueng-plueng jijak lintas .
brkop ateuh uteuen, hana geujaweueb.
Hagrid teungoh geuduek bak kurusi di luwa rumoh gobnyan; celana jih dan
lengan ka jigulong, dan jih teungoh jiboh kacang polong lam saboh mangkok nyang rayeuk.
“Hullo,” kheun jih, sira jisenyum. “Peureksaan yer nyang ka seuleusoe? Got watee peutamoeng jiep i?”
“Ya, silahkan,” kheun Ron, tapi Harry geukoh jih.
“Hana, kamoe ka terburu-buru. Hagrid, lon ka lon tanyong sapeu keu droeneuh. neuteupu
malam nyan ka meunang Norbert? Peue nyang hana aseng nyang teungoh gata meu'en kartu ngon .
deuh jih lagee?”
“Dunno,” kheun Hagrid deungon santai, “jih akan’ jicok jubah jih.”
Jih ji kalon awak nyan lhee deuh teukeujot dan ji peu ek alis mata.
“Kon that hana biasa, yeh meurumpok le that ureung lucu di Hog's Head —
nyan pub di miyup lam gampong. Mungken bin sidroe dealer naga, mungken jih? ulon
hana tom deuh muka jih, jih jikeubah tudung jih.”
Harry karam di bineh mangkok kacang polong. “Peue nyang droeneuh peugah haba ngon gobnyan .
teuntang, Hagrid? Peu na neu sebut Hogwarts sama sekali?”
“Mighta teuka,” kheun Hagrid, meuceu-ceu bak geucuba ingat.
“Yeah...jih jitanyong peu nyang lon peugot, an’ lon peugah bak jih lon gamekeeper disino...jih jitanyong a
bit tentang sorta makhluk yang lon cok lheuh...jadi lon peugah bak jih...an' lon peugah peu yang lon akan
sabee that meuheut nakeuh naga...an' watee nyan...lon jeut’ teuingat that get, 'seubab
jih sabe buyin' lon minuman...Mari kita lihat...yeah, lheuh nyan jih peugah jih na boh telor naga
an' kamoe jeut meu’en kartu fer nyan meunyo lon meuheut...tapi jih na pasti lon jeut lon tangani .
nyan, jih hana galak nyan ter go ter manapun rumoh tuha....Jadi lon peugah bak jih, lheuh Fluffy, saboh naga
akan mudah....”
“Dan peu jih — peu jih deuh tertarik keu Fluffy?” Harry geutanyong, geucuba .
jaga su jih tenang.
“Nyan — ya — padum boh anjing lhee ulee d’yeh meurumpok, bahkan sekitar .
Hogwarts? Jadi lon peugah bak jih, Fluffy nyan saboh boh kue meunyo yeh teupeu kiban cara peutente jih
down, jus’ meu'en jih bacut o' musik an' jih akan langsong off ter teungeut —”
Hagrid tiba-tiba deuh teukeujot.
“Lon harus'ta peugah yeh nyan!” geukheun le gobnyan. “Lupa lon peugah nyan! Hai -
pat gata tajak?”
Harry, Ron, dan Hermione hana saleng meututoe sama sekali sampoe awaknyan
teuka bak teumpat tamong, nyang deuh that lupie dan suram lheueh .
alasan.
“Kamoe ka meujak u Dumbledore,” kheun Harry. “Hagrid geupeugah bak ureung aseng nyan .
cara lewat Fluffy, dan nyan Snape atawa Voldemort di miyup jubah nyan —
pasti mudah, sigo jih ka ji peugot Hagrid mabok. Lon cuma meuharap bak Dumbledore
peucaya keu geutanyoe. Firenze mungken akan mendukung geutanyoe meunyo Bane hana geutheun jih. Dipat
Kanto Dumbledore nyan?”
Awaknyan jikeumalon ban sikeulileng, lagée jiharap jikalon saboh tanda nyang jitunyok awaknyan u uneuen .
arah. They had never been told where Dumbledore lived, nor did they know
Soe-soe nyang ka geu-utus jak kalon gobnyan.
“Geutanyoe hanya haroh —” Harry mulai, tapi saboh su tiba-tiba meu-ulang-ulang di linteung .
bale.
