Harry geujak u pesta akhe thon sidroe malam nyan. Gobnyan na
ka jimat lé Madam Pomfrey nyang ka ji-ulang-ulang, ji-ukheue keu jibri keu jih saboh .
checkup terakhir, jadi Aula Besar ka peunoh. Nyan dihias di luwa bak .
