Ravenclaw ngon Hufflepuff teungoh geupeuraya rhet Slitherin, “geutanyoe peureulee .
bacut ubah hiasan.”
Gobnyan geupoh jaroe. Lam siat, gantungan ijo jeuet keu mirah .
dan pirak ka jeuet keu méuh; uleue Slytherin nyang rayeuk that nyan gadôh dan saboh uleue nyang manyang .
Singa Griffindor geucok teumpat jih. Snape teungoh geumat jaroe Profesor McGonagall,
deungon senyuman nyang teumakot, paksa. Jih jiteumee mata Harry dan Harry jiteupeu sigra bahwa
Perasaan Snape keu jih hana meu ubah saboh jot pih. Nyoe hana ji khawatirkan Harry. Nyan
deuh jih lagee udep akan kembali normal thon ukeu, atawa normal lagee awai
na di Hogwarts.
Nyan keuh malam nyang paleng get lam udep Harry, leubeh get nibak meunang bak Quidditch,
atawa Natal, atawa peugot troll gunong...jih hana akan pernah, pernah tuwoe
malamnyo.
Harry karap tuwoe bahwa hasee ujian mantong akan teuka, tapi teuka .
awaknyan jipeubuet. To their great surprise, both he and Ron passed with good marks;
Hermione, teunte, na nilai nyang paleng get lam thon-thon phon. Bahkan Neville geukikis
through, his good Herbology mark making up for his abysmal Potions one. Awaknyan
ka geuharap Goyle, nyang karab saban bangai ngon gobnyan nyang jeuhet, mungken
ji-bh, tapi jih ka lewat, pih. Nyan keuh saboh male, tapi lagee kheun Ron, droeneuh hana jeut
na mandum lam udep.
